name: Lepak.TV
tag_list: videos, sharing, watch, lepak, lepak-tv, malaysian
overview: Founded in February 2008, Lepak.TV is a new and exciting Malaysian Community site that brings together everyone by watching and sharing videos and getting media exposure mainly across Malaysia and Asia. Tons of people come to lepak.tv to watch great original programming, but that’s not the end of it. we give people the chance to broadcast their videos to the world, we call this sharing entertainment. Viewers get to see first hand information regarding happenings around them may it be funny videos, bloopers, comedy skids, latest news, etc. We also serve as an informational tool for viewers in all age groups. Sharing videos with your family and friends has never been easier.
